                                <td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">Task&lt;OverlayResult&gt;</td>
                                <td class="p-3 text-muted-foreground">Opens a slide-in panel from the specified edge with component <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-foreground">T</code>.</td>
